             deposed that he met the Deceased and former Evidence, and heard the Deceased say, stay here while I go and call him up; that he went up the Court and knockt very hard. 
               <persName id="t17200602-16-person102">
                  Mary 
                  Benson 
               <interp inst="t17200602-16-person102" type="surname" value="Benson"></interp>
